1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,770 --> 00:01:40,940
[Her Fantastic Adventures]

3
00:01:41,039 --> 00:01:42,190
Get lost!

4
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:46,210
With such lousy skills, you dare to stop me?

5
00:01:47,110 --> 00:01:49,180
They're just too polite to hit you.

6
00:01:53,630 --> 00:01:54,470
Get up.

7
00:02:03,230 --> 00:02:05,430
Young Master, we've added more guards at the villa

8
00:02:05,430 --> 00:02:06,640
to prevent Young Master Shaoyi from running away.

9
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:09,030
Send Shaoyi to Jizhou Academy.

10
00:02:09,270 --> 00:02:09,960
Okay.

11
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,550
Bring Miss Gu here.

12
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:15,310
I have a tailor coming to take her measurements and make some clothes.

13
00:02:15,310 --> 00:02:16,110
Young Master,

14
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:18,910
you're not really planning to propose to Miss Gu, are you?

15
00:02:18,910 --> 00:02:21,430
Proposing was your idea, not mine.

16
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,980
Young Master, don't take this the wrong way,

17
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:25,280
but you and Miss Gu

18
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:27,550
aren't a good match.

19
00:02:27,550 --> 00:02:31,120
Whether we're suitable or not, I have my own judgment.

20
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,760
Why are you always staring at me?

21
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:41,360
Do I look like a plate of food?

22
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:42,200
Qiao.

23
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:46,490
You've grown up and look just like your mother.

24
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,290
Then she must be a great beauty.

25
00:02:50,070 --> 00:02:51,070
The buns are cold.

26
00:02:51,150 --> 00:02:52,270
Dongxi.

27
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:54,630
Master.

28
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,360
Have Da warm them up.

29
00:02:56,670 --> 00:02:57,550
No need.

30
00:02:57,630 --> 00:02:58,950
Cold vegetarian buns taste better,

31
00:02:58,950 --> 00:03:00,440
and I'm only having one.

32
00:03:02,220 --> 00:03:04,450
[Episode 3]

33
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:08,640
Take your time eating.

34
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:10,160
No one's going to snatch it from you.

35
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:12,000
Master! Master!

36
00:03:27,150 --> 00:03:29,350
What are you two whispering about?

37
00:03:29,420 --> 00:03:32,350
Young Master Duan invited you to the Duan Residence.

38
00:03:36,390 --> 00:03:38,840
Qiao, can't you be a bit more reserved?

39
00:03:39,110 --> 00:03:40,790
Why did he invite me to the Duan Residence?

40
00:03:40,790 --> 00:03:43,560
He said he got a tailor to make you some clothes.

41
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:45,430
Why can't the clothes be made at home?

42
00:03:45,430 --> 00:03:47,560
Maybe he wants you to choose the fabric yourself.

43
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,320
Well,

44
00:03:48,470 --> 00:03:49,990
they didn't clarify

45
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:55,000
whether the proposal is happening or not.

46
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:58,150
Then it's happening.

47
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,550
Why?

48
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:03,600
Qiao, listen to me.

49
00:04:03,670 --> 00:04:05,470
About you and Young Master Duan,

50
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:08,560
It seems like the Gu family is taking the initiative.

51
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:10,190
In reality, it's indeed you.

52
00:04:10,390 --> 00:04:11,450
Exactly, exactly.

53
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,870
But think about this.

54
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:16,110
After that big incident,

55
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:18,060
almost everyone in Changqing

56
00:04:18,060 --> 00:04:19,380
knows about it.

57
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:22,470
Few young masters dare to propose to you.

58
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:24,280
Now, you and Young Master Duan

59
00:04:24,280 --> 00:04:26,670
finally have a chance.

60
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:29,260
You must hold on to it.

61
00:04:31,510 --> 00:04:34,520
But it's not good for me to be too forward.

62
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:36,370
There's nothing wrong with it.

63
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:37,850
I'm not old-fashioned.

64
00:04:37,990 --> 00:04:40,240
You getting married is what matters most.

65
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,640
I'll follow your advice.

66
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:45,000
Going to their house to make clothes

67
00:04:45,230 --> 00:04:46,880
is the best opportunity.

68
00:04:46,990 --> 00:04:50,670
Turn this fake proposal into a real one.

69
00:04:54,950 --> 00:04:56,790
Just consider it a way

70
00:04:57,030 --> 00:04:59,430
to settle all this love and resentment.

71
00:04:59,990 --> 00:05:00,920
What did you say?

72
00:05:01,630 --> 00:05:03,310
Nothing.

73
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:06,260
It means a wish.

74
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:07,400
Okay.

75
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:09,240
I'm glad you understand.

76
00:05:09,790 --> 00:05:10,920
Take your time eating.

77
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,630
I'll go confirm

78
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:15,220
your visit to the Duan Residence.

79
00:05:21,550 --> 00:05:23,430
For poor Gu Qingqiao and her father,

80
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:26,320
I'll thicken my skin.

81
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:33,710
In the kitchen, he fell for the young lady at first sight

82
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:35,540
and couldn't help

83
00:05:35,750 --> 00:05:37,590
but hold her in his arms.

84
00:05:37,990 --> 00:05:41,720
The loyal guard witnessed this moment,

85
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:42,840
realizing

86
00:05:43,150 --> 00:05:46,400
that his master had met his destiny.

87
00:05:46,750 --> 00:05:48,810
Although it was their first meeting,

88
00:05:49,030 --> 00:05:51,760
Young Master Leng decided to marry the young lady

89
00:05:51,790 --> 00:05:53,790
and brought her to his residence three days later

90
00:05:53,790 --> 00:05:57,550
to continue their romance.

91
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,500
I really

92
00:06:00,710 --> 00:06:03,590
am a genius.

93
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:14,910
I made it for you

94
00:06:14,990 --> 00:06:16,390
knowing you were coming.

95
00:06:17,670 --> 00:06:19,280
I can't come empty-handed, right?

96
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:20,420
Is this for me?

97
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,330
Who else could it be for?

98
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,200
Where did you get it?

99
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,600
Knowing you love novels,

100
00:06:25,670 --> 00:06:27,270
I spent a lot to buy it for you.

101
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:28,730
Shaoyi, you're so nice.

102
00:06:29,670 --> 00:06:31,040
If you become my aunt,

103
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,510
I'll buy you novels every day.

104
00:06:32,510 --> 00:06:33,800
Are you that eager?

105
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,120
Of course.

106
00:06:35,470 --> 00:06:37,880
Or are you eager for me to make you snacks every day?

107
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:39,600
These snacks are really good.

108
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:40,800
It's a pity

109
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:42,360
I won't have them for a while.

110
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,360
Why not?

111
00:06:43,510 --> 00:06:45,000
I can make snacks and have Yuanhua deliver them

112
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:47,150
to the Duan Residence every day.

113
00:06:47,270 --> 00:06:48,880
I'll be leaving Changqing for a while.

114
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:50,159
Where are you going?

115
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:51,409
To find your father?

116
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:54,030
Duan Yu insists on sending me to Jizhou Academy.

117
00:06:54,030 --> 00:06:55,420
Jizhou Academy?

118
00:06:56,070 --> 00:06:57,530
Then when will you be back?

119
00:06:58,350 --> 00:06:59,320
I don't know.

120
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:01,320
Maybe a year, maybe two.

121
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:02,690
After you leave,

122
00:07:03,300 --> 00:07:05,430
I'll have one less friend to play with.

123
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,360
Don't worry.

124
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,000
I'll write to you.

125
00:07:09,340 --> 00:07:10,480
Madam Zhang.

126
00:07:12,910 --> 00:07:14,310
What are you doing?

127
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,800
Nothing.

128
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:22,080
Madam Zhang, crooked eyebrows are in fashion this year in Changqing?

129
00:07:23,230 --> 00:07:24,160
No, no, My Lady.

130
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:26,110
You startled me.

131
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:28,560
So, what brings you here?

132
00:07:28,710 --> 00:07:29,800
Well,

133
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:32,270
can I borrow your cosmetics?

134
00:07:35,870 --> 00:07:37,400
What are you planning to do?

135
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:39,200
You'll find out soon enough.

136
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:41,550
Why do you like Duan Yu?

137
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:42,940
There must be a reason.

138
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,350
No reason.

139
00:07:45,110 --> 00:07:47,640
Liking him has been my wish for two lifetimes.

140
00:07:47,700 --> 00:07:54,470
[Wine]

141
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,840
He's not as good at martial arts as I am.

142
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:50,770
He can't beat me.

143
00:07:53,150 --> 00:07:55,000
What does martial arts skill have to do with anything?

144
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:58,080
A wild horse being tamed by me

145
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:59,280
is so romantic.

146
00:07:59,650 --> 00:08:08,570
[Wine]

147
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,330
I think you're out of your mind.

148
00:08:03,190 --> 00:08:04,250
Hand me the mirror.

149
00:08:10,110 --> 00:08:10,840
How is it?

150
00:08:11,310 --> 00:08:12,600
Gu Qingqiao,

151
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,130
are you out of your mind?

152
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:15,910
It's hideous.

153
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:17,840
With your current look,

154
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,470
forget about walking on the street,

155
00:08:19,470 --> 00:08:21,600
no one would recognize you

156
00:08:21,870 --> 00:08:23,040
even if you walked out of Changqing openly.

157
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:24,970
Would you go out looking like this?

158
00:08:28,710 --> 00:08:30,030
Don't wipe it off.

159
00:08:30,210 --> 00:08:31,160
It's hideous.

160
00:08:37,850 --> 00:08:40,330
My Lady, the snacks you wanted are ready.

161
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:42,840
Pack the snacks in the food box and send them to the Duan Residence.

162
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,080
Are they for Young Master Duan?

163
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:44,960
No.

164
00:08:45,110 --> 00:08:46,560
They're for Duan Shaoyi.

165
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,350
What are the stories in the books

166
00:08:48,350 --> 00:08:49,510
that Young Master Shaoyi sent?

167
00:08:49,510 --> 00:08:52,550
They tell about countless couples,

168
00:08:52,750 --> 00:08:54,630
but not all have happy endings.

169
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:58,150
My Lady, you and Young Master Duan will definitely have a happy ending.

170
00:08:58,150 --> 00:08:58,920
Hurry up.

171
00:08:59,070 --> 00:08:59,920
Yes.

172
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:03,520
Wha... What's wrong?

173
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:05,960
My Lady, look at your face.

174
00:09:06,870 --> 00:09:09,120
What's wrong with my face?

175
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:11,390
No pimples. No styes.

176
00:09:11,470 --> 00:09:13,400
Aren't you going to the Duan Residence today?

177
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:15,320
You should go looking pretty.

178
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:18,160
Dongxi, I'm not used to heavy makeup.

179
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:19,950
Usually,

180
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:22,270
I just go for a natural look with a bit of lipstick.

181
00:09:22,270 --> 00:09:23,320
Natural look?

182
00:09:23,950 --> 00:09:26,080
This is the first time I've heard that.

183
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:27,470
How about this?

184
00:09:27,470 --> 00:09:28,960
I'll get you a face veil.

185
00:09:29,430 --> 00:09:31,160
That's something to consider.

186
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:36,450
[Duan Residence]

187
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:43,810
What are you looking at?

188
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:47,620
Isn't it popular for ancient people to wear face veils?

189
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,910
Am I not pulling it off well?

190
00:09:51,230 --> 00:09:53,030
Turn your faces away, everyone.

191
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,560
Turn your faces away.

192
00:09:57,110 --> 00:09:57,960
Xing Si.

193
00:09:58,710 --> 00:09:59,440
Tu Jia.

194
00:10:05,670 --> 00:10:07,200
Do I need to turn away too?

195
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:12,230
I was just joking with you guys.

196
00:10:12,430 --> 00:10:14,750
I did put on makeup seriously,

197
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:16,830
but I only want you to see it.

198
00:10:16,950 --> 00:10:18,830
You look great with or without makeup.

199
00:10:18,830 --> 00:10:21,700
You're better off without the veil.

200
00:10:22,870 --> 00:10:25,260
Young Master Duan, you are so sweet.

201
00:10:25,280 --> 00:10:27,480
Miss Gu, please.

202
00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:32,900
What's with the eagle?

203
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:36,400
It's our family emblem.

204
00:10:37,190 --> 00:10:38,390
I don't understand.

205
00:10:39,190 --> 00:10:42,350
Why do you have so many weapons here?

206
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:45,790
Our family is famous for the Qilin Bow.

207
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:47,520
15 years ago,

208
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:50,560
my father, Duan Sheng, led our men to attack the Sacred Blood Sect

209
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:53,270
but was severely injured by their leader.

210
00:10:53,430 --> 00:10:55,840
My brother, Duan Yan,

211
00:10:56,350 --> 00:10:58,150
was also injured protecting me.

212
00:10:58,310 --> 00:10:59,310
Soon after,

213
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:01,920
my father passed away.

214
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:04,650
And my brother took over as head of the family.

215
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:08,040
After years of hard work, we restored

216
00:11:08,110 --> 00:11:09,910
the Duan family's former glory.

217
00:11:10,550 --> 00:11:12,950
These weapons are just

218
00:11:13,160 --> 00:11:16,000
some of the spoils of war from our family's victories.

219
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:18,110
But this is just

220
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:19,780
the tip of the iceberg.

221
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,980
You're a martial arts hero.

222
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:25,040
Why are you involved in the Changqing Chamber of Commerce?

223
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:26,200
The Duan family has many businesses;

224
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,730
someone has to manage them.

225
00:11:29,280 --> 00:11:30,910
You can shoot arrows;

226
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,230
I can throw discus.

227
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:34,420
Doesn't that make us a perfect match?

228
00:11:35,070 --> 00:11:36,160
Discus?

229
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:38,690
What weapon is that?

230
00:11:41,160 --> 00:11:43,040
It's not a weapon,

231
00:11:43,230 --> 00:11:45,360
more like a piece of sports equipment.

232
00:11:45,510 --> 00:11:47,040
Forgive my ignorance.

233
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:49,760
Our Duan family is familiar with seventy-two types of weapons,

234
00:11:49,760 --> 00:11:51,790
but I've never heard of a discus.

235
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:54,110
Which school or sect does it belong to?

236
00:11:55,160 --> 00:11:59,310
It's probably from sports schools

237
00:11:59,390 --> 00:12:00,680
or sports teams.

238
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:03,230
Stop talking about my skills.

239
00:12:03,230 --> 00:12:05,230
Can I ask you a small favor?

240
00:12:05,230 --> 00:12:05,990
Miss Gu,

241
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:07,600
feel free to ask.

242
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:09,120
I want to see you

243
00:12:10,710 --> 00:12:11,570
shoot an arrow.

244
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:24,270
So handsome.

245
00:12:25,550 --> 00:12:28,840
Miss Gu, I haven't even shot the arrow yet.

246
00:12:28,990 --> 00:12:32,480
I was talking about your perfect profile,

247
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:35,870
strong arms, and sexy waistline.

248
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,510
Amazing!

249
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:48,790
Right on target.

250
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:52,080
You should definitely join the national team!

251
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:56,390
The Sacred Blood Sect leader, Ying Tian,

252
00:12:56,390 --> 00:12:58,760
was killed by this Qilin Bow.

253
00:13:00,030 --> 00:13:02,840
Uncle Duan was still so strong despite his age!

254
00:13:02,990 --> 00:13:06,000
My father was only thirty then.

255
00:13:09,880 --> 00:13:11,840
Only thirty?

256
00:13:12,040 --> 00:13:14,040
My mistake.

257
00:13:15,950 --> 00:13:16,920
What's this

258
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:18,880
weird-looking weapon?

259
00:13:19,020 --> 00:13:20,420
Is it used by the Axe Gang?

260
00:13:20,560 --> 00:13:23,350
This is the Sacred Blood Sect's Yuanyang Axes

261
00:13:23,550 --> 00:13:25,240
from the Xuanwu Hall.

262
00:13:26,510 --> 00:13:28,680
How do you use it?

263
00:13:28,830 --> 00:13:30,960
Like an axe?

264
00:13:36,510 --> 00:13:38,240
This is the Duan family shrine.

265
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:41,080
During festivals and happy events,

266
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:43,480
I come here to pay respects to my ancestors.

267
00:13:44,870 --> 00:13:46,230
So,

268
00:13:46,750 --> 00:13:48,080
bringing me here is like

269
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:50,440
introducing me to your parents?

270
00:13:52,270 --> 00:13:55,440
You're That's one way to put it...

271
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:06,760
Uncle Duan, although we've never met,

272
00:14:07,660 --> 00:14:09,280
it's a pleasure to know you.

273
00:14:11,160 --> 00:14:12,710
Let me kowtow to you.

274
00:14:16,590 --> 00:14:19,190
I hope you bless me and Duan Yu

275
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:21,960
with a long and happy life together.

276
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:25,070
Auntie Duan, don't worry.

277
00:14:25,150 --> 00:14:27,200
I'll take good care of Duan Yu.

278
00:14:28,670 --> 00:14:29,840
Brother Duan,

279
00:14:30,110 --> 00:14:32,510
may your spirit

280
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:37,270
bless us with children soon.

281
00:14:37,350 --> 00:14:40,710
Miss Gu, my brother is still alive,

282
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:44,750
and isn't it a bit early to talk about having children?

283
00:14:45,630 --> 00:14:48,350
Can't you pretend you didn't hear that?

284
00:14:49,150 --> 00:14:49,820
And

285
00:14:49,880 --> 00:14:51,790
can you not speak when I'm making a wish?

286
00:14:51,790 --> 00:14:53,450
It won't come true otherwise.

287
00:14:54,230 --> 00:14:54,920
Miss Gu,

288
00:14:55,390 --> 00:14:58,050
aren't you curious about the Sacred Blood Sect?

289
00:15:00,640 --> 00:15:01,970
Why should I be curious?

290
00:15:03,640 --> 00:15:04,430
Nothing.

291
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:05,650
Just asking.

292
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:09,070
But there's something I want to confirm with you.

293
00:15:09,070 --> 00:15:11,030
Miss Gu, go ahead.

294
00:15:12,220 --> 00:15:17,550
Have you never seen me before?

295
00:15:18,280 --> 00:15:21,640
Meeting at the Gu Residence was the first time.

296
00:15:24,670 --> 00:15:27,360
Then why did you propose to me

297
00:15:27,800 --> 00:15:29,240
at our first meeting?

298
00:15:30,630 --> 00:15:31,950
Xing Si mentioned it.

299
00:15:33,390 --> 00:15:35,670
Who said it doesn't matter.

300
00:15:36,400 --> 00:15:37,870
Can't you consider it

301
00:15:38,350 --> 00:15:41,390
as a unique bond between us?

302
00:15:42,830 --> 00:15:44,500
Why are you smiling? Did I say something wrong?

303
00:15:44,500 --> 00:15:46,910
It really is a unique bond.

304
00:15:47,030 --> 00:15:50,480
Of course, because I'm a unique girl.

305
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:53,620
You really are unique.

306
00:15:55,920 --> 00:15:56,760
Duan Yu.

307
00:15:57,490 --> 00:15:59,080
This is the nicest thing anyone's said to me

308
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:00,790
since I came to Changqing.

309
00:16:01,190 --> 00:16:02,790
You're really slick and sly.

310
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:05,320
Slick and sly?

311
00:16:07,490 --> 00:16:08,490
Slick and sly...

312
00:16:08,520 --> 00:16:10,520
It means you are very smart

313
00:16:10,550 --> 00:16:12,430
and tactful.

314
00:16:12,630 --> 00:16:13,630
Miss Gu,

315
00:16:13,940 --> 00:16:16,890
you are also a very slick and sly girl.

316
00:16:23,600 --> 00:16:24,960
Duan Yu,

317
00:16:25,310 --> 00:16:27,620
thank you for having me at your house.

318
00:16:28,070 --> 00:16:30,760
A heart for you.

319
00:16:32,290 --> 00:16:36,640
[Duan Yu, thank you for having me at your house. A heart for you]

320
00:16:40,680 --> 00:16:41,590
Is that true?

321
00:16:42,990 --> 00:16:44,230
Prepare a carriage to Duan Residence.

322
00:16:44,230 --> 00:16:47,790
[Duan Residence]

323
00:16:54,760 --> 00:16:56,200
Miss Du, Young Master is not home.

324
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:58,040
Impossible. My miss wants to see Young Master Duan.

325
00:16:58,040 --> 00:16:59,100
-Miss. Miss.
-Go away!

326
00:16:59,100 --> 00:17:01,030
My young master is really not home.

327
00:17:01,190 --> 00:17:02,990
You grew up in Changqing, right?

328
00:17:04,560 --> 00:17:05,720
I guess so.

329
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:08,630
I had a serious illness earlier

330
00:17:09,190 --> 00:17:11,250
and don't remember much from before.

331
00:17:11,280 --> 00:17:12,150
What illness?

332
00:17:12,359 --> 00:17:13,490
Have you recovered?

333
00:17:13,510 --> 00:17:15,079
I don't know what it was,

334
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:19,190
but Doctor Dong said

335
00:17:19,310 --> 00:17:20,400
I'm fine now.

336
00:17:21,950 --> 00:17:23,079
That's good to hear.

337
00:17:23,589 --> 00:17:25,470
So,

338
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:28,109
what do you like to do besides work?

339
00:17:28,470 --> 00:17:30,600
I like playing chess with myself.

340
00:17:30,720 --> 00:17:31,750
Playing chess?

341
00:17:32,310 --> 00:17:35,270
Anything else?

342
00:17:35,630 --> 00:17:37,520
Practicing martial arts and reading.

343
00:17:37,520 --> 00:17:40,520
Practicing martial arts and reading all day must be boring.

344
00:17:40,520 --> 00:17:41,980
Don't you like traveling?

345
00:17:42,360 --> 00:17:45,220
Like wandering the Martial Arts World with a sword?

346
00:17:45,630 --> 00:17:47,250
Books say that

347
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:49,330
great martial artists

348
00:17:49,520 --> 00:17:51,230
love to roam the world.

349
00:17:51,350 --> 00:17:52,430
I'm not a hero

350
00:17:52,760 --> 00:17:54,680
and rarely leave Changqing.

351
00:17:55,310 --> 00:17:56,440
Why not?

352
00:17:56,560 --> 00:17:57,680
The world is big,

353
00:17:57,790 --> 00:17:59,390
with so many fun things to do.

354
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:01,840
How about this:

355
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:03,550
after we get married,

356
00:18:03,670 --> 00:18:05,310
I'll take you traveling every day.

357
00:18:05,310 --> 00:18:06,240
Married?

358
00:18:06,600 --> 00:18:07,480
Yes,

359
00:18:08,190 --> 00:18:09,070
married.

360
00:18:09,390 --> 00:18:10,350
In Changqing,

361
00:18:10,350 --> 00:18:12,480
everyone knows that Young Master Duan

362
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:15,620
is talented and handsome, elegant and extraordinary.

363
00:18:15,870 --> 00:18:19,480
Do you think he genuinely likes my lady?

364
00:18:19,590 --> 00:18:21,320
Your young lady,

365
00:18:21,320 --> 00:18:22,830
the first time she met our young master,

366
00:18:22,830 --> 00:18:24,470
she clung to him and wouldn't let go.

367
00:18:24,470 --> 00:18:25,320
Nonsense!

368
00:18:25,670 --> 00:18:28,390
It was your young master who held on to my young lady.

369
00:18:28,390 --> 00:18:30,040
If you slander my young lady again,

370
00:18:30,040 --> 00:18:31,100
I will... I will...

371
00:18:38,470 --> 00:18:40,020
[Duan Residence]

372
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:16,590
Here.

373
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:28,830
Duan Yu, what are you doing?

374
00:19:29,140 --> 00:19:31,230
Look at your feet.

375
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:38,160
Are you going to change shoes for me?

376
00:19:38,390 --> 00:19:39,450
If you're willing.

377
00:19:40,800 --> 00:19:42,350
Why wouldn't I be?

378
00:19:45,720 --> 00:19:46,430
Okay.

379
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:50,200
Wait,

380
00:19:50,550 --> 00:19:52,710
isn't it said that

381
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:56,000
men shouldn't see a woman's feet before marriage?

382
00:19:56,920 --> 00:19:57,600
Sorry,

383
00:19:58,190 --> 00:19:59,590
that was inappropriate.

384
00:20:01,150 --> 00:20:02,710
Inappropriate? Not at all.

385
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:04,670
I'm just ticklish.

386
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:06,320
I can change them myself.

387
00:20:06,320 --> 00:20:07,080
Okay.

388
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:16,150
Sorry.

389
00:20:16,590 --> 00:20:17,790
I'm being rude again.

390
00:20:25,390 --> 00:20:28,030
Miss Gu has been frail since childhood.

391
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:29,760
Although she seems fine now,

392
00:20:29,760 --> 00:20:31,630
she's actually weak.

393
00:20:31,800 --> 00:20:34,320
I heard Miss Gu came back to life after dying.

394
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:36,320
Is that true?

395
00:20:36,390 --> 00:20:37,350
Absolutely.

396
00:20:37,430 --> 00:20:40,280
I personally checked her pulse both when she left and when she returned.

397
00:20:40,280 --> 00:20:42,920
You can ask anyone at the Gu Residence.

398
00:20:43,070 --> 00:20:45,240
How do you explain her coming back to life?

399
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:46,830
Have you met it before?

400
00:20:46,830 --> 00:20:49,510
It's the first time I've encountered such a thing.

401
00:20:49,510 --> 00:20:52,110
Not everyone gets this kind of luck.

402
00:20:52,750 --> 00:20:55,440
She must have already crossed

403
00:20:55,550 --> 00:20:57,000
the River Styx.

404
00:20:57,390 --> 00:21:01,590
Maybe she came back because she couldn't leave her father behind.

405
00:21:02,350 --> 00:21:04,720
Does she seem the same as before?

406
00:21:04,840 --> 00:21:07,120
She looks the same,

407
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:10,640
but it seems she's forgotten many things.

408
00:21:10,830 --> 00:21:13,960
Also, she talks strangely.

409
00:21:15,310 --> 00:21:17,560
Could it have been a case of feigned death?

410
00:21:17,560 --> 00:21:18,630
Impossible.

411
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:22,050
She hasn't been quite right mentally since she revived.

412
00:21:33,150 --> 00:21:34,670
Master, you are here!

413
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:36,490
Business is good today.

414
00:21:36,960 --> 00:21:37,670
Yes.

415
00:21:39,430 --> 00:21:40,310
What is this?

416
00:21:41,120 --> 00:21:42,910
Miss Gu designed a new menu,

417
00:21:42,950 --> 00:21:44,960
and Chef Da taught us a few new dishes.

418
00:21:44,960 --> 00:21:47,040
Business is looking good.

419
00:21:47,670 --> 00:21:49,280
If the food festival goes well,

420
00:21:49,280 --> 00:21:51,630
our Qingfeng Restaurant will be the top restaurant

421
00:21:51,630 --> 00:21:53,510
in Changqing.

422
00:21:54,260 --> 00:21:58,240
[Wine]

423
00:21:54,320 --> 00:21:56,880
Top restaurant?

424
00:21:57,000 --> 00:21:58,840
I doubt it.

425
00:21:59,920 --> 00:22:00,720
Manager Yang,

426
00:22:01,040 --> 00:22:03,880
what brings you to our Qingfeng Restaurant?

427
00:22:04,040 --> 00:22:06,640
I heard you privately approached Chairman Duan

428
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:09,220
to host a food festival at Qingfeng Restaurant.

429
00:22:09,220 --> 00:22:12,600
Such a good thing, and you didn't share it with us?

430
00:22:12,920 --> 00:22:14,120
Once it's confirmed,

431
00:22:14,160 --> 00:22:16,000
we will, of course, invite all the managers

432
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:18,240
to join us at Qingfeng Restaurant.

433
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,670
Thank you.

434
00:22:21,550 --> 00:22:24,950
However, I also plan to suggest to Chairman Duan

435
00:22:25,120 --> 00:22:27,510
to hold the food festival at my Chunfeng Restaurant.

436
00:22:27,510 --> 00:22:30,470
Our Chunfeng Restaurant has been famous in Changqing for decades.

437
00:22:30,470 --> 00:22:33,310
I'm sure the chairman and members won't oppose it,

438
00:22:33,720 --> 00:22:34,430
right?

439
00:22:35,280 --> 00:22:36,680
I'm afraid Chairman Duan

440
00:22:37,510 --> 00:22:39,760
won't agree so easily.

441
00:22:40,080 --> 00:22:40,790
Is that so?

442
00:22:40,910 --> 00:22:41,720
Fine,

443
00:22:41,960 --> 00:22:44,280
let's

444
00:22:45,160 --> 00:22:46,360
wait and see.

445
00:22:47,750 --> 00:22:49,070
Manager Yang,

446
00:22:49,950 --> 00:22:51,280
I won't see you out then.

447
00:22:56,190 --> 00:22:56,950
Miss Gu,

448
00:22:57,190 --> 00:22:58,630
you fell into the water earlier.

449
00:22:58,630 --> 00:23:00,710
Here, drink this medicine.

450
00:23:01,640 --> 00:23:03,230
It will ward off the cold and warm you up.

451
00:23:03,230 --> 00:23:05,080
I've asked the servants to prepare several doses.

452
00:23:05,080 --> 00:23:08,340
Take them back to your residence and use them for a few days.

453
00:23:10,800 --> 00:23:12,440
On that rainy day...

454
00:23:15,210 --> 00:23:16,160
Thank you.

455
00:23:16,230 --> 00:23:17,160
You're welcome.

456
00:23:19,400 --> 00:23:20,120
Yes.

457
00:23:24,430 --> 00:23:25,470
What's this about?

458
00:23:25,470 --> 00:23:28,110
Didn't we agree to take your measurements for new clothes?

459
00:23:28,110 --> 00:23:29,110
Now?

460
00:23:29,280 --> 00:23:30,740
In front of so many people?

461
00:23:31,040 --> 00:23:32,300
It's not appropriate.

462
00:23:33,680 --> 00:23:34,810
Everyone, leave us.

463
00:23:34,910 --> 00:23:36,070
Yes.

464
00:23:40,230 --> 00:23:41,430
No need for the trouble.

465
00:23:41,430 --> 00:23:42,990
I'll have Dongxi bring over a piece of clothing.

466
00:23:42,990 --> 00:23:44,950
You can use it for the measurements.

467
00:23:44,950 --> 00:23:45,590
Yes.

468
00:23:46,800 --> 00:23:47,860
That will work too.

469
00:23:51,550 --> 00:23:52,600
Braised pork?

470
00:23:53,310 --> 00:23:55,500
Your cook can make braised pork?

471
00:23:55,680 --> 00:23:57,000
Don't mention braised pork.

472
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:59,000
Young Master had your braised pork

473
00:23:59,110 --> 00:24:00,470
at your house

474
00:24:00,910 --> 00:24:02,520
and had our cook try to replicate it,

475
00:24:02,520 --> 00:24:03,400
but

476
00:24:03,480 --> 00:24:05,240
he couldn't get it right.

477
00:24:05,280 --> 00:24:06,480
Bring your cook over,

478
00:24:06,560 --> 00:24:07,140
and I'll teach him.

479
00:24:07,140 --> 00:24:07,910
No need.

480
00:24:08,040 --> 00:24:09,710
I already dismissed him.

481
00:24:10,710 --> 00:24:14,160
So you made the braised pork?

482
00:24:16,510 --> 00:24:17,560
I made it.

483
00:24:17,920 --> 00:24:19,950
Miss Gu, try it and see how it tastes.

484
00:24:26,280 --> 00:24:27,210
It's delicious.

485
00:24:36,670 --> 00:24:38,540
I'm so hungry I could start cursing.

486
00:24:38,540 --> 00:24:39,160
Got it.

487
00:24:39,280 --> 00:24:42,010
I'll have Da make braised pork for you right away.

488
00:24:43,080 --> 00:24:43,880
Qiao,

489
00:24:44,400 --> 00:24:47,790
it's better for young ladies to eat less braised pork.

490
00:24:48,190 --> 00:24:50,720
I know, you're worried about my cholesterol.

491
00:24:54,560 --> 00:24:55,760
Don't look at me like that.

492
00:24:55,760 --> 00:24:56,820
Forget what I said.

493
00:24:59,670 --> 00:25:01,670
Today I went to Qingfeng Restaurant

494
00:25:01,800 --> 00:25:03,880
to get them ready for the food festival.

495
00:25:03,880 --> 00:25:04,480
Looks like

496
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:06,240
I'll need to train them tomorrow.

497
00:25:06,240 --> 00:25:08,030
Training? What's that?

498
00:25:08,230 --> 00:25:09,960
You wouldn't understand even if I explained.

499
00:25:09,960 --> 00:25:12,280
Anyway, before I get married,

500
00:25:12,560 --> 00:25:14,240
I'll help you

501
00:25:14,320 --> 00:25:15,850
get everything sorted out.

502
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:21,550
What if the food festival

503
00:25:21,550 --> 00:25:24,130
isn't held at our Qingfeng Restaurant in the end?

504
00:25:24,130 --> 00:25:26,360
Won't all our efforts be wasted?

505
00:25:27,830 --> 00:25:29,230
Have you heard anything?

506
00:25:30,350 --> 00:25:32,840
Today at Qingfeng Restaurant, I ran into Yang Chunfeng.

507
00:25:32,840 --> 00:25:34,190
He said he wants Chairman Duan

508
00:25:34,190 --> 00:25:36,510
to host the food festival at his Chunfeng Restaurant.

509
00:25:36,510 --> 00:25:37,630
If

510
00:25:37,710 --> 00:25:39,960
Chairman Duan agrees,

511
00:25:40,440 --> 00:25:43,040
we'd be working for nothing.

512
00:25:44,550 --> 00:25:46,240
Don't worry.

513
00:25:46,360 --> 00:25:49,760
Duan Yu won't agree to Yang Chunfeng's proposal because of me.

514
00:25:49,760 --> 00:25:51,000
Are you that sure?

515
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:54,600
Father, don't underestimate your daughter

516
00:25:54,630 --> 00:25:57,120
and her confidence and charm.

517
00:25:57,240 --> 00:25:58,240
Miss Dongxi said

518
00:25:58,310 --> 00:26:00,200
Miss Gu was gravely ill and died,

519
00:26:00,800 --> 00:26:02,840
but then revived in the mourning hall.

520
00:26:02,840 --> 00:26:04,000
To verify this,

521
00:26:04,200 --> 00:26:05,350
I specifically sought out Doctor Dong,

522
00:26:05,350 --> 00:26:07,480
who has treated the Gu family for years.

523
00:26:07,480 --> 00:26:08,390
He confirmed that

524
00:26:08,390 --> 00:26:10,990
he'd been prescribing medicine for Miss Gu since childhood.

525
00:26:10,990 --> 00:26:13,440
Miss Gu has been frail since childhood.

526
00:26:13,520 --> 00:26:14,910
Although she seems fine now,

527
00:26:14,910 --> 00:26:16,240
she's actually weak.

528
00:26:16,280 --> 00:26:18,310
I heard Miss Gu came back to life after dying.

529
00:26:18,310 --> 00:26:20,480
Is that true?

530
00:26:20,600 --> 00:26:21,830
Absolutely.

531
00:26:21,950 --> 00:26:24,670
I personally checked her pulse both when she left and when she returned.

532
00:26:24,670 --> 00:26:27,200
You can ask anyone at the Gu Residence.

533
00:26:27,400 --> 00:26:29,360
But he attributed her revival

534
00:26:29,480 --> 00:26:31,020
to his superb medical skills.

535
00:26:31,020 --> 00:26:33,940
Also, according to the Wuyi Guards,

536
00:26:34,030 --> 00:26:35,270
Miss Gu showed no internal strength

537
00:26:35,270 --> 00:26:36,960
during the incident,

538
00:26:37,520 --> 00:26:38,640
indicating

539
00:26:38,760 --> 00:26:41,390
she is an ordinary woman

540
00:26:42,040 --> 00:26:44,900
uninterested in the various factions of Changqing

541
00:26:45,470 --> 00:26:47,320
and unaware of the Sacred Blood Sect.

542
00:26:47,320 --> 00:26:50,110
When I deliberately gave her the wrong information about the origin of the Yuanyang Axes,

543
00:26:50,110 --> 00:26:51,550
You can shoot arrows,

544
00:26:51,980 --> 00:26:53,540
You can shoot arrows,

545
00:26:53,950 --> 00:26:55,120
and I can throw a discus.

546
00:26:55,120 --> 00:26:56,760
Aren't we a perfect match?

547
00:26:57,120 --> 00:26:59,470
Gosh, drawing a bow is really tough.

548
00:26:59,670 --> 00:27:01,200
Why wouldn't I?

549
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:03,960
Young Master.

550
00:27:04,240 --> 00:27:08,000
Are you suggesting that Gu Qingqiao is connected to the Sacred Blood Sect?

551
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:10,670
I suspect she might be the Star of Rebellion.

552
00:27:11,430 --> 00:27:12,600
Prophesy has it that

553
00:27:12,670 --> 00:27:15,390
the appearance of the Star of Rebellion would cause heavenly anomalies

554
00:27:15,390 --> 00:27:17,750
and aid the resurgence of the Sacred Blood Sect,

555
00:27:17,750 --> 00:27:20,030
leading to widespread devastation

556
00:27:20,590 --> 00:27:22,960
and the downfall of the Duan family.

557
00:27:23,990 --> 00:27:25,650
As a member of the Duan family,

558
00:27:25,750 --> 00:27:27,750
I must take precautions.

559
00:27:28,150 --> 00:27:30,680
Miss Gu took the first incense at Shangqing Temple,

560
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:32,520
and then there were celestial phenomena,

561
00:27:32,520 --> 00:27:34,840
which made you suspicious.

562
00:27:34,960 --> 00:27:35,860
I helped her change her shoes

563
00:27:35,860 --> 00:27:38,430
to check if she had the mark on her foot.

564
00:27:39,040 --> 00:27:40,700
Actually, I'm just ticklish.

565
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:42,280
I can change them myself.

566
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:44,280
Miss Gu

567
00:27:45,000 --> 00:27:46,460
seems too scatterbrained

568
00:27:46,510 --> 00:27:47,920
to be the Star of Rebellion.

569
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:49,650
It might just be a coincidence.

570
00:27:50,510 --> 00:27:53,880
Or perhaps she's playing dumb

571
00:27:54,030 --> 00:27:56,110
and is actually very slick and sly?

572
00:27:56,110 --> 00:27:56,830
What?

573
00:27:57,670 --> 00:27:59,920
It means that she's playing dumb

574
00:28:00,040 --> 00:28:01,720
but actually being very clever.

575
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:04,270
You learned this from Miss Gu?

576
00:28:04,390 --> 00:28:05,080
Yes.

577
00:28:05,880 --> 00:28:08,960
Yes, but it feels quite satisfying to say.

578
00:28:09,110 --> 00:28:11,480
Besides, I deliberately went into the wrong room

579
00:28:11,480 --> 00:28:13,040
and placed letters about the Sacred Blood Sect

580
00:28:13,040 --> 00:28:14,150
on the desk,\

581
00:28:14,760 --> 00:28:16,000
but she didn't care.

582
00:28:16,760 --> 00:28:18,900
Look, this is what she wrote:

583
00:28:22,380 --> 00:28:25,370
[Duan Yu, thank you for having me at your house. A heart for you]

584
00:28:23,750 --> 00:28:25,490
Her handwriting is so bad.

585
00:28:26,320 --> 00:28:26,950
And this.

586
00:28:27,080 --> 00:28:28,780
What is this monster holding?

587
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:30,670
Is this a weapon?

588
00:28:30,980 --> 00:28:32,160
Or something else?

589
00:28:32,720 --> 00:28:34,240
You're so ignorant.

590
00:28:34,630 --> 00:28:37,510
It says "a heart".

591
00:28:34,750 --> 00:28:37,200
[Duan Yu, thank you for having me at your house. A heart for you]

592
00:28:38,080 --> 00:28:39,470
This is a Japanese weapon,

593
00:28:39,470 --> 00:28:41,280
commonly known as shuriken.

594
00:28:41,840 --> 00:28:43,190
A heart?

595
00:28:43,750 --> 00:28:45,190
Is this a challenge letter?

596
00:28:45,190 --> 00:28:46,630
And what about this heart?

597
00:28:46,620 --> 00:28:48,530
[Duan Yu, thank you for having me at your house. A heart for you]

598
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:49,260
This red part won't be poisonous, right?

599
00:28:50,320 --> 00:28:51,640
Even if it is,

600
00:28:52,200 --> 00:28:53,320
it's fine.

601
00:28:55,190 --> 00:28:56,390
Mom, I'm leaving.

602
00:28:57,040 --> 00:28:59,240
Chunjiao, remember to go for your check-up in the afternoon.

603
00:28:59,240 --> 00:29:01,350
Here, drink this fish soup. It's good for your bones.

604
00:29:01,350 --> 00:29:03,030
I'm not drinking it. I'm sick of it.

605
00:29:03,030 --> 00:29:04,500
Hurry up, it's for your calcium.

606
00:29:04,500 --> 00:29:05,220
Drink it.

607
00:29:05,240 --> 00:29:07,430
Drinking this early in the morning will make me vomit.

608
00:29:07,430 --> 00:29:08,800
Then vomit and drink again.

609
00:29:08,800 --> 00:29:09,680
Hurry up.

610
00:29:09,880 --> 00:29:11,320
Are you really my mom?

611
00:29:11,350 --> 00:29:12,640
You're a top-up gift.

612
00:29:13,580 --> 00:29:15,110
Hurry up.

613
00:29:15,110 --> 00:29:16,720
With the time you've wasted, you could've finished two bowls.

614
00:29:16,720 --> 00:29:17,750
Two bowls?

615
00:29:18,800 --> 00:29:19,560
Be good.

616
00:29:27,310 --> 00:29:28,220
Okay?

617
00:29:28,310 --> 00:29:29,850
You need to get your strength back, Chunjiao.

618
00:29:29,850 --> 00:29:36,360
[Glory of Meat]

619
00:29:29,920 --> 00:29:30,900
In your world,

620
00:29:30,920 --> 00:29:33,040
all I do is train and eat.

621
00:29:33,070 --> 00:29:34,350
There's a third thing:

622
00:29:34,520 --> 00:29:35,520
win the championship.

623
00:29:35,520 --> 00:29:36,320
Go for it.

624
00:29:37,000 --> 00:29:38,610
Chunjiao! Chunjiao!

625
00:29:38,760 --> 00:29:39,750
Pick up the phone.

626
00:29:39,750 --> 00:29:40,520
Phone.

627
00:29:41,720 --> 00:29:42,630
Phone.

628
00:29:43,830 --> 00:29:45,530
I need to answer my mom's call.

629
00:29:45,750 --> 00:29:46,470
My Lady.

630
00:29:46,840 --> 00:29:48,100
My Lady, what's wrong?

631
00:29:53,310 --> 00:29:54,440
I'm exhausted.

632
00:29:55,320 --> 00:29:56,910
Did you have a nightmare again?

633
00:29:56,910 --> 00:29:58,350
I'll get you some water.

634
00:30:13,990 --> 00:30:14,990
You again. What do you want?

635
00:30:14,990 --> 00:30:16,510
You were out the whole day.

636
00:30:16,820 --> 00:30:18,150
Can't I come and see you?

637
00:30:18,270 --> 00:30:20,320
I'm really tired today.

638
00:30:20,440 --> 00:30:21,610
Please go back to your cellar.

639
00:30:21,610 --> 00:30:23,430
You're really ungrateful.

640
00:30:24,550 --> 00:30:26,720
After seeing Duan Yu, you lose your head

641
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:27,830
and your stance.

642
00:30:27,950 --> 00:30:29,210
Say whatever you want.

643
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:30,240
My stance is firm.

644
00:30:30,440 --> 00:30:32,280
Is it truly firm or just a show?

645
00:30:32,520 --> 00:30:34,230
You're so annoying.

646
00:30:34,350 --> 00:30:35,480
If you don't leave,

647
00:30:35,550 --> 00:30:36,610
I'll call for help.

648
00:30:37,870 --> 00:30:40,390
I was going to tell you

649
00:30:40,560 --> 00:30:42,510
the whereabouts of the Four Treasures,

650
00:30:42,510 --> 00:30:44,160
but I've decided not to.

651
00:30:44,520 --> 00:30:46,050
Trying to deceive me again?

652
00:30:47,920 --> 00:30:49,120
You said before

653
00:30:49,120 --> 00:30:50,510
you didn't know where the Four Treasures are.

654
00:30:50,510 --> 00:30:51,570
Couldn't it be that

655
00:30:51,910 --> 00:30:53,030
I lied?

656
00:30:53,120 --> 00:30:55,080
Lie to whomever you want.

657
00:30:55,280 --> 00:30:57,280
If I don't sleep, I'll have dark circles.

658
00:30:57,280 --> 00:30:58,600
Some people just can't tell

659
00:30:58,600 --> 00:31:01,680
who's a friend and who's an enemy.

660
00:31:03,150 --> 00:31:05,010
This is one of the Four Treasures?

661
00:31:06,590 --> 00:31:07,430
Yes.

662
00:31:07,840 --> 00:31:10,240
This is the Mantra Sect's sacred artifact,

663
00:31:10,870 --> 00:31:12,800
the Nine-turn melodious bell.

664
00:31:13,120 --> 00:31:15,390
This is just my electronic watch.

665
00:31:15,560 --> 00:31:17,150
How did it become the Nine-turn melodious bell?

666
00:31:17,150 --> 00:31:18,560
I have no reason

667
00:31:18,600 --> 00:31:19,950
to joke or lie to you now.

668
00:31:20,080 --> 00:31:22,750
I've never seen the Nine-turn melodious bell.

669
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:25,460
How would I know if it's fake?

670
00:31:26,590 --> 00:31:28,670
This is the Nine-turn melodious bell from the Four Treasures.

671
00:31:28,670 --> 00:31:29,760
The patterns on the Nine-turn melodious bell

672
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:31,080
change over time.

673
00:31:31,430 --> 00:31:32,720
And if you touch here,

674
00:31:32,910 --> 00:31:35,800
it speaks like a deity.

675
00:31:36,950 --> 00:31:38,760
The current time

676
00:31:38,840 --> 00:31:40,600
is 9:11 PM.

677
00:31:40,720 --> 00:31:42,310
Only such an extraterrestrial object

678
00:31:42,310 --> 00:31:44,390
could have such magical functions.

679
00:31:44,950 --> 00:31:46,360
Look at its texture,

680
00:31:46,480 --> 00:31:48,010
neither leather nor metal.

681
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:51,350
I know.

682
00:31:51,720 --> 00:31:53,750
This is plastic.

683
00:31:54,040 --> 00:31:55,720
Do you want it?

684
00:31:56,160 --> 00:31:57,310
Yes.

685
00:31:59,760 --> 00:32:01,350
I knew you wouldn't give it to me so easily.

686
00:32:01,350 --> 00:32:02,470
Of course not.

687
00:32:03,790 --> 00:32:04,860
Unless

688
00:32:06,040 --> 00:32:07,630
you do something for me.

689
00:32:08,190 --> 00:32:09,920
It's definitely nothing good.

690
00:32:10,760 --> 00:32:11,890
Let me make it clear,

691
00:32:12,320 --> 00:32:14,600
I won't do anything illegal.

692
00:32:14,760 --> 00:32:17,040
The chairman has already decided to hold the festival at our place.

693
00:32:17,040 --> 00:32:19,000
There's no need to discuss this further.

694
00:32:19,000 --> 00:32:20,670
How can there be no need for discussion?

695
00:32:20,670 --> 00:32:21,800
Why is that?

696
00:32:21,910 --> 00:32:23,150
Tell me why.

697
00:32:23,270 --> 00:32:24,560
We are serving meat dishes.

698
00:32:24,290 --> 00:32:25,900
[Changqing Chamber of Commerce]

699
00:32:24,590 --> 00:32:25,550
You're a vegetarian restaurant.

700
00:32:25,550 --> 00:32:27,210
Why are you getting involved?

701
00:32:27,870 --> 00:32:28,600
Miss Gu.

702
00:32:28,840 --> 00:32:29,920
You want to see me?

703
00:32:30,240 --> 00:32:32,910
Are you trying to catch the Mantra Sect disciple?

704
00:32:32,910 --> 00:32:34,240
I can help you catch him.

705
00:32:34,560 --> 00:32:35,820
Let's talk in private.

706
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:37,720
Catch the Mantra Sect disciple?

707
00:32:37,720 --> 00:32:39,050
What do you mean by that?

708
00:32:39,480 --> 00:32:42,300
It's very difficult to capture him.

709
00:32:42,560 --> 00:32:44,120
Now, the whole city knows

710
00:32:44,240 --> 00:32:47,670
the government is looking for the Right Guardian of the Mantra Sect.

711
00:32:47,670 --> 00:32:49,920
If we spread the word

712
00:32:50,040 --> 00:32:51,640
that the Right Guardian will

713
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:54,360
surrender to the government during the food festival,

714
00:32:54,360 --> 00:32:55,800
both the Right Guardian

715
00:32:55,830 --> 00:32:57,590
and Mantra Sect disciple

716
00:32:57,710 --> 00:33:00,960
will be curious to see who is impersonating him.

717
00:33:01,080 --> 00:33:02,060
You are smart.

718
00:33:02,280 --> 00:33:03,680
Can it work?

719
00:33:03,820 --> 00:33:04,710
It can work,

720
00:33:04,830 --> 00:33:07,320
but I could also set the location at Chunfeng Restaurant.

721
00:33:07,320 --> 00:33:08,270
No no no.

722
00:33:08,710 --> 00:33:10,320
It must be at Qingfeng Restaurant,

723
00:33:10,320 --> 00:33:13,110
because it's the perfect place.

724
00:33:31,960 --> 00:33:33,720
Look, I've drawn it.

725
00:33:37,240 --> 00:33:38,310
What is this?

726
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:39,940
This is Yong'an Street.

727
00:33:39,940 --> 00:33:41,080
Can't you tell?

728
00:33:41,960 --> 00:33:43,230
This is Qingfeng Restaurant.

729
00:33:43,230 --> 00:33:44,430
This is the pawnshop.

730
00:33:44,600 --> 00:33:47,110
This is Dye Street. And across is the rice store.

731
00:33:47,110 --> 00:33:48,800
Isn't it all clear?

732
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:51,000
Yes.

733
00:33:51,320 --> 00:33:55,230
Miss Gu, you should stick to talking.

734
00:33:56,230 --> 00:33:57,720
Don't worry about the details.

735
00:33:57,720 --> 00:33:59,520
This is just about the location.

736
00:34:00,240 --> 00:34:01,630
I've thought it through.

737
00:34:01,630 --> 00:34:05,110
The front of Qingfeng Restaurant is spacious and busy,

738
00:34:05,230 --> 00:34:07,480
good for blending in plainclothes officers.

739
00:34:07,480 --> 00:34:11,630
The alleyways at the back are narrow and winding,

740
00:34:11,750 --> 00:34:13,320
perfect for ambushes and surrounding the place.

741
00:34:13,320 --> 00:34:16,350
The rooftops in the area are uneven,

742
00:34:16,520 --> 00:34:17,400
great for...

743
00:34:22,830 --> 00:34:23,679
Come on.

744
00:34:24,120 --> 00:34:25,760
Your drawing skills

745
00:34:26,120 --> 00:34:27,840
are amazing!

746
00:34:28,400 --> 00:34:30,730
Just a minor skill, not worth mentioning.

747
00:34:30,790 --> 00:34:31,790
Please continue.

748
00:34:33,830 --> 00:34:35,150
Where was I?

749
00:34:35,239 --> 00:34:37,590
You were talking about observing discreetly.

750
00:34:37,590 --> 00:34:38,639
That's right.

751
00:34:38,900 --> 00:34:40,639
It's easy to observe discreetly.

752
00:34:40,639 --> 00:34:43,920
My Qingfeng Restaurant's advantageous terrain for both offense and defense

753
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:46,070
is unmatched by Chunfeng Restaurant.

754
00:34:46,190 --> 00:34:48,320
Aren't you afraid of leaking the plan?

755
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:49,320
How could that be?

756
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:50,840
This is our plan.

757
00:34:52,159 --> 00:34:55,679
And you are someone who wants to propose to me.

758
00:34:56,830 --> 00:34:58,070
Xing Si said it.

759
00:34:59,640 --> 00:35:01,120
Can't you just agree?

760
00:35:02,720 --> 00:35:04,380
Regarding the food festival,

761
00:35:04,520 --> 00:35:07,280
I had many concerns when Manager Gu first brought it up,

762
00:35:07,280 --> 00:35:09,680
thinking it was unwise to hold such an event

763
00:35:09,800 --> 00:35:11,680
during the Mantra Sect's unrest.

764
00:35:11,790 --> 00:35:14,110
That's because he is incompetent and inconsiderate.

765
00:35:14,110 --> 00:35:16,250
If it were at my Chunfeng Restaurant,\

766
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:18,800
everything would be organized perfectly.

767
00:35:18,950 --> 00:35:21,000
The organizer must prioritize the bigger picture,

768
00:35:21,000 --> 00:35:23,060
ensuring the safety of all attendees

769
00:35:23,320 --> 00:35:26,310
and assisting the government in capturing the Mantra Sect disciple.

770
00:35:26,310 --> 00:35:28,160
Then the government officials should be fed and accommodated,

771
00:35:28,160 --> 00:35:29,870
which will surely incur losses.

772
00:35:29,870 --> 00:35:32,260
Gu Xingwu, the Vice President of Changqing Chamber of Commerce,

773
00:35:32,260 --> 00:35:34,270
and all staff of Qingfeng Restaurant will fully cooperate.

774
00:35:34,270 --> 00:35:34,990
Wait.

775
00:35:35,760 --> 00:35:38,190
What if this important event fails?

776
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:40,480
Then, wouldn't you have to resign from the vice president position?

777
00:35:40,480 --> 00:35:41,510
Deal.

778
00:35:41,750 --> 00:35:43,880
Qiao, there's nothing else.

779
00:35:44,030 --> 00:35:45,560
I'm just worried about you.

780
00:35:45,640 --> 00:35:48,310
What if something goes wrong

781
00:35:48,790 --> 00:35:50,120
with the food festival?

782
00:35:50,550 --> 00:35:52,680
It's a small matter for me to lose face,

783
00:35:52,750 --> 00:35:53,600
but what if it affects

784
00:35:53,600 --> 00:35:55,470
our family's livelihood

785
00:35:55,590 --> 00:35:57,400
or your future

786
00:35:57,520 --> 00:35:58,720
marriage prospects?

787
00:35:58,790 --> 00:36:00,670
It's not as serious as you think.

788
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:03,510
Involving the Mantra Sect is dangerous.

789
00:36:03,630 --> 00:36:05,310
Don't worry so much.

790
00:36:05,470 --> 00:36:06,590
I've discussed everything

791
00:36:06,590 --> 00:36:08,150
with Young Master Duan;

792
00:36:08,550 --> 00:36:10,010
there won't be any danger.

793
00:36:10,280 --> 00:36:12,510
As the saying goes,

794
00:36:13,430 --> 00:36:15,800
"There are always more solutions than problems."

795
00:36:15,800 --> 00:36:17,830
We must overcome every hurdle.

796
00:36:18,240 --> 00:36:21,280
Competitions are not just about strength

797
00:36:21,990 --> 00:36:23,590
but also mental resilience.

798
00:36:24,390 --> 00:36:27,880
Never get discouraged

799
00:36:28,070 --> 00:36:29,470
before giving your best.

800
00:36:30,350 --> 00:36:32,200
Believe in yourself,

801
00:36:32,400 --> 00:36:33,790
and you'll succeed.

802
00:36:34,630 --> 00:36:38,240
The heavens will not forsake the diligent.

803
00:36:40,030 --> 00:36:41,230
Life is about

804
00:36:41,980 --> 00:36:45,360
overcoming challenges one after another.

805
00:36:46,550 --> 00:36:49,190
Even if I'm not around in the future,

806
00:36:49,760 --> 00:36:51,680
don't give up easily.

807
00:36:53,280 --> 00:36:54,790
Persist in your dreams;

808
00:36:56,640 --> 00:37:02,760
they will reward your efforts.

809
00:37:04,670 --> 00:37:06,400
Remember my words.

810
00:37:10,560 --> 00:37:11,510
Dad.

811
00:37:12,680 --> 00:37:14,440
Qiao, what's wrong?

812
00:37:16,350 --> 00:37:17,230
Nothing.

813
00:37:17,720 --> 00:37:19,750
I just thought of someone.

814
00:37:21,280 --> 00:37:22,000
Who?

815
00:37:22,440 --> 00:37:24,560
Who made my Qiao so sad?

816
00:37:27,030 --> 00:37:29,550
Nothing, let's get back to business.

817
00:37:29,990 --> 00:37:30,800
This is an opportunity

818
00:37:30,800 --> 00:37:33,330
to make Qingfeng Restaurant famous in one go.

819
00:37:33,390 --> 00:37:34,390
We must seize it.

820
00:37:36,830 --> 00:37:39,230
The younger generation surpasses the old,

821
00:37:39,350 --> 00:37:40,750
making us proud.

822
00:37:41,640 --> 00:37:45,170
This is what they call "the waves behind drive the waves ahead."

823
00:37:45,600 --> 00:37:47,350
Now I've grown up.

824
00:37:47,960 --> 00:37:50,200
You've always made sacrifices for me,

825
00:37:51,520 --> 00:37:53,750
and now it's my turn to protect you.

826
00:37:55,360 --> 00:37:56,240
Give me five.

827
00:38:02,880 --> 00:38:06,420
[Qingfeng Restaurant]

828
00:38:05,870 --> 00:38:06,560
Forward!

829
00:38:06,420 --> 00:38:10,470
[Glory of Meat]

830
00:38:09,590 --> 00:38:10,640
Turn back.

831
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:12,910
Look to the right!

832
00:38:13,350 --> 00:38:14,480
Look ahead!

833
00:38:15,070 --> 00:38:16,710
My Lady, our delivery staff

834
00:38:16,750 --> 00:38:19,550
has been trained according to your instructions.

835
00:38:19,560 --> 00:38:20,470
Not bad.

836
00:38:20,950 --> 00:38:22,350
Please give your speech.

837
00:38:24,350 --> 00:38:27,240
Get ready with your oilskin coats and rain hats.

838
00:38:27,390 --> 00:38:28,910
Qingfeng Restaurant's delivery service

839
00:38:28,910 --> 00:38:30,270
is unstoppable in any weather.

840
00:38:30,270 --> 00:38:32,320
Our slogan is

841
00:38:32,560 --> 00:38:33,910
"The Glory of Meat!"

842
00:38:34,470 --> 00:38:35,950
Our motto is

843
00:38:36,160 --> 00:38:39,840
